            <h4><strong>MISSION:</strong> At the higher level, we hope that Stale Buddy will help reduce the amount of food waste in the United States and proactively aid in optimizing user purchases, recipes, and perishable goods to prevent buying goods in excess. It will also reduce the risk of consuming contaminated food by making users aware of the expiration dates of their products.</h4><br>
            <p> The purpose of this project is to provide users an effective way of tracking the expiration dates of perishable goods. A major problem in todayâ€™s society is food waste. In the United States alone the estimated number of consumers who throw out items close to or past the expiration dates is an astonishing 84%, this results in over 100 billion pounds of goods going to waste. An attributing factor to this problem is many consumers purchase goods in excess. This is not because consumers intend to be wasteful, but because many consumers do not have time throughout the week to make multiple trips to their super markets and because it is a more time efficient to go a fewer number of times.</p>
